 village who used to make up ointments and all that sort of thing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5265435\charrsid3212931  for - from the herbs that grew }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 
