\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6429687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 Do you remember your birthday being different from any other day?
