\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6429687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 Was it mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2506258 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 Yes. Two hundred children. I can see the board now - every day it was marked with how many children you see. And the littl
e playground was so small - and the boy - the boys then wore half boots because they went to sea when they were only nine or ten, and they would wear these little half boots up to school and we had our legs kicked, very small playground. So we didn't have
 much - life.
