\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6429687 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 How long was this before you were actually married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2506258 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 That was the - that was the evening we were married. Mm.
