e was - yes, a yachtsman until he went into the Navy. He was - he - most of our fishermen at that time had joined the Naval Reserve - which - would would give them perhaps a month's - work, a month or two in the - worst time of the year, the wintertime wh
en it was a slack time they would do this month's drink once in a while you'd have to go abo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6365406\charrsid3212931 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14897221\charrsid3212931 
