arry the water, and we put that could in water what we called from - a shoot here in the middle of the village, but the nurse didn't think that that was clean enough and so he had to bring down the - turn after turn of - it was the first of June, a very h
ot summer, very hot day but - Jack was born. Fairs Saturday. And Saturday afternoon or evening really before he was born. But that was the only help that I had from Jack was to bringing the water.
